lead_paragraph: French financial authorities are considering investigating how Qatar was awarded the 2022 soccer World Cup, financial prosecutor Eliane Houlette said on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: French Prosecutor Considering Qatar 2022 World Cup Investigation
